<pc>。</pc>庶人耒耜<num value="20">二十</num>具<pc>、</pc>鍤<num value="2">二</num>具<pc>，</pc>木為刃<pc>。</pc>主藉田縣令<measure quantity="1" unit="people">
<num value="1">一</num>人</measure>
<pc>，</pc>具朝服<pc>，</pc>當耕時立田側<pc>，</pc>畢乃退<pc>。</pc>畿甸諸縣令先期集<pc>，</pc>以常服陪耕所<pc>，</pc>耆艾<measure quantity="20" unit="people">
